c STABLE HYDRO SYSTEM WITH 2 TURBINES (NO WARNINGS)

SYSTEM
    ELEM HW AT 1

    ELEM C1 LINK 1 2
    ELEM C2 LINK 2 3
    ELEM C3 LINK 3 4

    JUNCTION AT 4

    ELEM C4A LINK 4 5
    ELEM C5A LINK 5 6
    ELEM T1 LINK 6 7
    ELEM TW1 AT 7

    ELEM C4B LINK 4 8
    ELEM C5B LINK 8 9
    ELEM T2 LINK 9 10
    ELEM TW2 AT 10

    NODE 1 ELEV 500
    NODE 2 ELEV 495
    NODE 3 ELEV 490
    NODE 4 ELEV 480

    NODE 5 ELEV 470
    NODE 6 ELEV 460
    NODE 7 ELEV 450

    NODE 8 ELEV 470
    NODE 9 ELEV 460
    NODE 10 ELEV 450
FINISH

